00:24:45.190 --> 00:24:48.200
The Toneybee Institute paid for it.

00:24:48.200 --> 00:24:51.640
It had a curt, upturned nose
that looked smug and out

00:24:51.640 --> 00:24:54.190
of place beside the lazing sedans

00:24:54.190 --> 00:24:58.010
