parked on our block.

00:24:58.010 --> 00:25:01.770
Being inside the Volvo felt
like we were in public.

00:25:01.770 --> 00:25:04.300
None of us could bring
ourselves to speak.

00:25:04.300 --> 00:25:07.990
We were all too humbled
by the leather interiors.

00:25:10.270 --> 00:25:14.740
My mother, in the driver's seat,
adjusted her rearview mirror.

00:25:14.740 --> 00:25:18.960
My younger sister, Callie, kept
playing with the automatic windows

00:25:18.960 --> 00:25:21.670
